---
title: Bengal Fish Curry with Basmati Rice
description: Our rich Bengal curry is a stellar way to bring fish to your dinner table. It's full of aromatic flavours and ready in just 30 minutes. To make the perfect rice, avoid the temptation to lift the lid before it's ready – it cooks in its own steam!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d4101419fe95c000c2bedd4-7e6b3068.jpg
